<section class="faq" id="faqs">
  <div class="faq__inner">
    <div class="faq__content">
      <span class="faq__eyebrow">FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="faq__title">Answers to Your Questions</h2>
      <p class="faq__text">Get a quick overview of how PetTravelPK works before you reach out. If you still have questions, our team is ready to help directly.</p>
      <a class="faq__button" href="#contact">Contact Us</a>
    </div>

    <div class="faq__accordion" data-faq-accordion>
      <article class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__trigger" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="faq-item__question">Which countries do you ship pets to?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel" hidden>
          <div class="faq-item__panel-inner">
            We coordinate pet relocation to 50+ destinations worldwide, including North America, Europe, the Middle East, and Australia, depending on route rules and airline availability.
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__trigger" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="faq-item__question">What vaccinations does my pet need before travel?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel" hidden>
          <div class="faq-item__panel-inner">
            Vaccination requirements depend on the destination country and species. We guide you through the needed vaccines, health certificates, and timing so you stay compliant.
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__trigger" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="faq-item__question">How long does the import/export process take?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel" hidden>
          <div class="faq-item__panel-inner">
            Timelines vary by route, paperwork, and airline schedules. Simple relocations can move quickly, while more complex cases may take longer for approvals, testing, and booking.
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__trigger" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="faq-item__question">Do you handle all pet breeds, including exotic animals?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel" hidden>
          <div class="faq-item__panel-inner">
            Yes. We work with dogs, cats, birds, reptiles, and select exotic pets, subject to destination-country rules and airline acceptance policies.
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__trigger" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="faq-item__question">Is my pet insured during the journey?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel" hidden>
          <div class="faq-item__panel-inner">
            We can advise on travel insurance options and carrier best practices. Coverage details depend on the route, carrier, and the policy selected for your relocation.
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__trigger" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="faq-item__question">What is an IATA-approved crate and do I need one?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel" hidden>
          <div class="faq-item__panel-inner">
            An IATA-approved crate is an airline-compliant travel kennel designed for safety, ventilation, and size requirements. In most international relocations, yes, you will need one.
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__trigger" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="faq-item__question">Can I track my pet during travel?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel" hidden>
          <div class="faq-item__panel-inner">
            Yes. We keep you updated throughout the process and share status updates so you know where your pet is and what the next step will be.
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__trigger" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="faq-item__question">How do I get started with PetTravelPK?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel" hidden>
          <div class="faq-item__panel-inner">
            Start by contacting us with your pet’s details, destination, and travel dates. We’ll review the route, explain the paperwork, and guide you through the next steps.
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

